OL,3,CFinance worker 'drunkenly abused'
OL,4,Ccabin crew and passengers on flight
OL,6,FA finance worker who drunkenly abused
OL,7,Ffellow passengers and crew on board a
OL,8,Fflight from Mallorca to Gatwick
OL,9,FAirport has been sentenced.
OL,11,FHarrison Tilson, of Old Town, Lambeth,
OL,12,Fwas found guilty at Crawley
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court of assault by
OL,14,Fbeating, and for being drunk on board
OL,15,Fan aircraft contrary to the Air
OL,16,FNavigation Order.
