OL,3,CFinance worker 'drunkenly abused'
OL,4,Ccabin crew and passengers on flight
OL,6,FSussex Police said that the 33-year-
OL,7,Fold had abused passengers and staff on
OL,8,Fboard the flight before assaulting a
OL,9,Fmember of the cabin crew on 15 May
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FTilson was sentenced to a two-year
OL,13,Fcommunity order to complete 250 hours
OL,14,Fof unpaid work, 10 rehabilitation
OL,15,Factivity requirement (RAR) sessions
OL,16,Fand he was ordered to pay #1,800 in
OL,17,Fcompensation to the cabin crew worker
OL,18,Fand court costs of #1,500.
