OL,3,CFinance worker 'drunkenly abused'
OL,4,Ccabin crew and passengers on flight
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Sussex Police said:
OL,7,F"Tilson consumed three glasses of
OL,8,Fchampagne in the airport lounge prior
OL,9,Fto boarding. He later consumed a
OL,10,Ffurther three glasses of red wine on
OL,11,Fboard.
OL,13,F"His behaviour from the outset was
OL,14,Frude and abusive, swearing at fellow
OL,15,Fpassengers and crew.
OL,17,F"When the aircraft landed, he ignored
OL,18,Fthe instruction to stay seated and
OL,19,Fwent to the toilet while the plane was
OL,20,Ftaxiing to the terminal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
