PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F416A1730233706
OL,3,CFinance worker 'drunkenly abused'
OL,4,Ccabin crew and passengers on flight
OL,6,F"Tilson's behaviour was appalling. No
OL,7,Fcabin crew worker should have to
OL,8,Faccept being abused and assaulted as
OL,9,Fsimply part of the job.
OL,11,F"That is why we are determined to
OL,12,Fpursue prosecutions against those who
OL,13,Fbreak the law on board aircraft. For
OL,14,FTilson, this has proved to be an
OL,15,Fexpensive case.
OL,17,F"It should act as a warning to all
OL,18,Fpassengers about the risks of
OL,19,Fconsuming alcohol before boarding a
OL,20,Fflight or while on board."
